    "coffee": {
      "allocated": 1,
      "rationale": "Coffee funding offers higher monetary support ($600k) but is limited to 24-count bags and 4 weeks. If awarded, it consumes the single circular slot for coffee, potentially reducing seasonal produce exposure and affecting other categories negatively. Given the one-slot cap, the investment window and product specificity make coffee the high-impact, high-risk option. Recommend partial or no allocation if expected incremental profit is less than snacks due to longer coverage with snacks and broader reach across salty snacks for the 9-week period, though snack front-page requirement complicates allocation."
